OL,7,FA couple who repeatedly visited
OL,8,Frestaurants and racked up huge bills
OL,9,Fbefore leaving without paying have
OL,10,Fadmitted a string of offences.
OL,12,FBernard and Ann McDonagh left
OL,13,Frestaurants and other businesses out
OL,14,Fof pocket to the tune of more than
OL,15,F#2,000 through their actions, a court
OL,16,Fheard.
OL,18,FThe husband and wife entered guilty
OL,19,Fpleas to five counts of fraud when
OL,20,Fthey appeared at Magistrates' Court on
OL,21,FWednesday.
