OL,7,FA judge heard how they obtained food
OL,8,Fand drink for themselves and their
OL,9,Ffamily at a number of in south Wales
OL,10,Fon different occasions and left
OL,11,Fwithout paying their bills.
OL,13,FThe court heard the couple attended
OL,14,FBella Ciao restaurant in Castle Street
OL,15,Fin Swansea on April 19 this year.
OL,16,FThere they obtained food and drink for
OL,17,Fthemselves and their family to the
OL,18,Fvalue of #329.10 with "no intention of
OL,19,Fpaying for it."
